cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.CC, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the complexity of regular and star-free languages.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper involves analyzing the complexity of operations on languages.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper involves analyzing the complexity of boolean operations on languages.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper involves analyzing the complexity of language operations.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves analyzing the complexity of language operations in terms of information theory.
